00:00:00.620 --> 00:00:03.150
- [Voiceover] So let's say
that we have the equation

00:00:03.150 --> 00:00:07.220
negative seven x minus eight y

00:00:07.220 --> 00:00:09.710
is equal to 28.

00:00:09.710 --> 00:00:12.090
So this right over here,
this is a linear equation,

00:00:12.090 --> 00:00:14.220
it's in standard form,

00:00:14.220 --> 00:00:16.580
and what I want to do
with you in this video

00:00:16.580 --> 00:00:21.580
